parameters:
\SE\SE[115]Luna will be coming back soon... I wonder what
I'll do if she's grown up so much... \SE[115]It's been five
years... Five whole years.

\SE[120] She might have become a big shot in the city, and
she might find this countryside boring... \SE[100] If that's
the case, I'll be in trouble... Very much so...

\SE[14]... In that case, I need to make appropriate
preparations, right?

\SE[15]... Alright, let's practice that thing! \SE[58] I've
been told for a long time that it's better to practice after
all...!
↓立ち絵を非表示にするコマンドです。
これが動いている間は\SE[]関連は必要なし。

...It's me. I don't have any particularly outstanding
qualities... I'm just an ordinary person...

...No, that's not it! \. This is not the time to be feeling
down! \. Today, without fail, I have to make sure to become
a thing!! \! I don't have much time to practice that!!

\SE[19]\SM[pop]But I'm mentally prepared...! \Because the
time might come...! \!\SE[58]In life, \you never know what
might happen!

\SE[2]... Oh, that's right! \. I should have some backup
panties! \!\SE[22] It's always good to be prepared, you
know.

\F[laura_smile7]\FF[papan_normal]\AA[FF]What's wrong?
\C[23]Laura\C[0]. You seem to be in a great mood.

\F[laura_smile7]\FHehe~♪ Can you guess? Ehehe~ I won't tell
you~!

\F[laura_smile7]\FF[papan_normal]\AA[FF]Eh... Please tell
me... Papa is shocked...

\F[laura_smile7]\FF[mamamiya_normal]\AA[FF]Don't tease Papa
too much. Look, that child. The girl next door,
\C[23]Lunaroa\C[0]-chan. She left a year ago saying she'll
enroll in the school. She's coming back tomorrow, they say.

\F[laura_smile7]\FF[papan_normal]\AA[FF]Is that the daughter
who went as a scholarship student... She's studying magic at
Hoshikai Academy, right? ...That's amazing, isn't it?

\F[laura_smile6]\FF[mamamiya_normal]\AA[FF]This child, she
was so in love with Lunaroa-chan. When she was little, she
used to say, I'm going to marry Lunaroa! and wouldn't
listen... It's nostalgic, isn't it?

\F[laura_smile6]\FNo, that's not it! I still love her! We
promised to get married after we graduate!

Haha! Since two girls can't get married in this country,
we'll have to move to a place like Yurisene!

\F[laura_doya6]\FF[papan_normal]\AA[F]Then let's move! We'll
definitely get married!!

\F[laura_doya6]\FDon't provoke this child too much. Isn't it
about time for you? You're going to be teased by the boss
again, aren't you?

\F[laura_doya6]\FF[papan_normal]\AA[FF]Oh, I got it! Then,
I'll go work for the sake of my beloved family!
Well... I better do the laundry while I can.

\F[laura_smile1]\FF[mamamiya_normal]\AA[FF]... Oh my, we're
running low on firewood. What should we do?

\F[laura_smile3]\FF[mamamiya_normal]\AA[FF]Hmm, should I ask
her? But don't go too far, okay? And make sure to come back
before noon.

\F[laura_doya1]\FLeave it to me! I'll pick up the best
things for you!

\FF[mamamiya_normal]\AA[FF]You really have a lot of
energy... But it's already been 5 years, huh? Time flies
when you're getting older...

It's five years worth of correspondence with Lunaroa... My
treasure.

\SE[2]Ah, that's right. \SE[14]\SM[double]I'm pretty sure
it's around here...
\SE[29]I wonder if it's still too early to go to bed....
